All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AttackingSpell
Magic spells that do some sort of damage to a target
Concoction
Concoctions can affect health and mana of the target at the same time and additionally cast any number of spells
HealingSpell
Healing spells increase the targets health or mana
HealthPotion
HealthPotions increase the consumer's mana
MagicEffectRealization
This interface contains all the methods to realize various magic effects on an object.
MagicItem
MagicItems are items that can cause magic effects on other objects.
MagicLevel
Defines the various magic levels.
MagicSource
A MagicSource object can provide mana necesary to cause a magic effect
ManaPotion
A ManaPotion provides mana to its consumer
Potion
A potion has a specific magic effect on its consumer
ProtectingSpell
ProtectingSpell objects grant protection against a number of specific attacking spells
Scroll
A Scroll object contains a spell that can be read by someone.
Spell
A Spell object generates a magic effect on a target.
Tradeable
Tradeable objects can be traded and stored in inventories
Trader
Trader objects have an inventory in which they can store magic items.
Wizard
Wizard class objects are the primary actors in the game.
